name: __ENiagaraSystemSpawnSectionEndBehavior
doc: Defines options for system life cycle for the time after the section.

SetSystemInactive: / When the section ends the system is set to inactive which stops spawning but lets existing particles simulate until death.
Deactivate: / When the section ends the system's component is deactivated which will kill all existing particles.
None: / Does nothing when the section ends and allows the system to continue to run as normal.
